{"lc": 1, "type": "constructor", "id": ["langchain", "schema", "document", "Document"], "kwargs": {"metadata": {"Header 1": "**6\ufe0f\u20e3 Why only for the first card**"}, "page_content": "Your card style already has spacing **between cards**.  \nFile: **RecommendedCommunities.tsx**  \ncardContainer: {  \nmarginRight: theme.spacing.sm,  \n}  \nSo layout becomes:  \n| padding | Card1 | gap | Card2 | gap | Card3  \nIf we added marginLeft to **all cards**, you'd get double spacing.  \nSo we check:  \nindex === 0  \nMeaning:  \nonly the first card gets marginLeft", "type": "Document"}}